original_title: Legacy Fighting Alliance 83: Jackson vs. Chaulet
overview: This Pro MMA event was held at The Bomb Factory in Dallas, Texas on March 6th, 2020. Main event: Damon "The Leech" Jackson vs. Mauro Chaulet. Co-main event: Justin "The Tactician" Patterson vs. "Magic" Matt Dixon.
title: Legacy Fighting Alliance 83: Jackson vs. Chaulet
